rules.sql: SELECT DISTINCT p.patient_id,          p.first_name || ' ' || p.last_name AS patient_name,         ph.condition_name,         COALESCE(TO_VARCHAR(MAX(da.appointment_date)), 'Never') as last_annual_checkup  FROM HEALTH_DATA.PATIENTS p  INNER JOIN HEALTH_DATA.PATIENT_HEALTH ph ON p.patient_id = ph.patient_id  LEFT JOIN HEALTH_DATA.DR_APPOINTMENTS da ON p.patient_id = da.patient_id       AND da.appointment_type = 'ANNUAL_CHECKUP'       AND da.status = 'COMPLETED'      AND da.appointment_date >= DATEADD(year, -1, CURRENT_DATE())  WHERE ph.chronic_condition = TRUE     AND ph.treatment_status IN ('ACTIVE', 'MANAGED')  GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, ph.condition_name;

rules.sql: SELECT p.patient_id,        p.first_name || ' ' || p.last_name AS patient_name,        COUNT(DISTINCT ph.icd10_code) as condition_count,        MAX(da.appointment_date) as last_visit FROM HEALTH_DATA.PATIENTS p INNER JOIN HEALTH_DATA.PATIENT_HEALTH ph ON p.patient_id = ph.patient_id LEFT JOIN HEALTH_DATA.DR_APPOINTMENTS da ON p.patient_id = da.patient_id      AND da.status = 'COMPLETED' WHERE ph.chronic_condition = TRUE   AND ph.severity IN ('SEVERE', 'CRITICAL')   AND ph.treatment_status = 'ACTIVE' GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT ph.icd10_code) >= 2     AND (MAX(da.appointment_date) IS NULL          OR MAX(da.appointment_date) < DATEADD(month, -3, CURRENT_DATE()));

SELECT p.patient_id,          p.first_name || ' ' || p.last_name AS patient_name,          p.insurance_provider,          COUNT(ic.claim_id) as total_claims,          SUM(CASE WHEN ic.status = 'APPROVED' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as approved_claims,          ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN ic.status = 'APPROVED' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(ic.claim_id)), 2) as approval_rate   FROM HEALTH_DATA.PATIENTS p   INNER JOIN HEALTH_DATA.INSURANCE_CLAIMS ic ON p.patient_id = ic.patient_id   GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, p.insurance_provider   HAVING COUNT(ic.claim_id) >= 2       AND (SUM(CASE WHEN ic.status = 'APPROVED' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(ic.claim_id)) < 80;

SELECT p.patient_id,         p.first_name || ' ' || p.last_name AS patient_name,         ph.condition_name,         ph.severity,         COUNT(da.appointment_id) as visits_last_year,         MAX(da.appointment_date) as last_visit_date  FROM HEALTH_DATA.PATIENTS p  INNER JOIN HEALTH_DATA.PATIENT_HEALTH ph ON p.patient_id = ph.patient_id  LEFT JOIN HEALTH_DATA.DR_APPOINTMENTS da ON p.patient_id = da.patient_id       AND da.status = 'COMPLETED'      AND da.appointment_date >= DATEADD(year, -1, CURRENT_DATE())  WHERE ph.icd10_code LIKE 'E11%' -- Diabetes codes    AND ph.treatment_status = 'MANAGED'  GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, ph.condition_name, ph.severity  HAVING COUNT(da.appointment_id) < 4;

SELECT p.patient_id,         p.first_name || ' ' || p.last_name AS patient_name,         COUNT(da.appointment_id) as emergency_visits,         LISTAGG(DISTINCT ph.condition_name, '; ') as conditions  FROM HEALTH_DATA.PATIENTS p  INNER JOIN HEALTH_DATA.DR_APPOINTMENTS da ON p.patient_id = da.patient_id  LEFT JOIN HEALTH_DATA.PATIENT_HEALTH ph ON p.patient_id = ph.patient_id       AND ph.treatment_status IN ('ACTIVE', 'MANAGED')  WHERE da.appointment_type = 'EMERGENCY'    AND da.appointment_date >= DATEADD(month, -6, CURRENT_DATE())    AND da.status = 'COMPLETED'  GROUP BY p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name  HAVING COUNT(da.appointment_id) >= 2;
